{"tid":2244433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［九龍城區議會］民政處刪去民主派提出討論反對港康碼文件 不過批准討論如何推出港康碼","createTime":"2020-10-15T12:52:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T12:58:25.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e33abe857420758b1ea73867a46e2a96ad4e09f5","tid":2244433,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:52:30.000Z","msg":"九龍城區議會下午開會，民政處雙重標準，民主派提出討論反對港康碼，但遭處方刪去文件。早前DQ黃之鋒參選資格的九龍城民政事務專員蔡敏君，更拉隊離開。但民建聯提出討論施政報告的期望，包括推出港康碼和推動大灣區合作，則獲准在會上討論。本身是律師、民主黨黃國桐批評，當局的做法是政治打壓和「淪亡到咁嘅地步」，「公務員政治中立蕩然無存」，令香港政治制度完全崩潰，形容為十分傷感的局面。<br />\n<br />\n在今次的會議中，民主派有5份文件被指不符合《區議會條例》，更遭民政處刪去，包括訂立「動物保護法」、反對通識教科書強制送審、反對港康碼、關注12港人和要求教育局撤回取消教師註冊決定<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078190?fbclid=IwAR1xGL9CFUqt-_MQ-YAY1dJUYI9LWKzFkb8znpKxybLC4y5T9ZVcpY4awY8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078190%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1xGL9CFUqt-_MQ-YAY1dJUYI9LWKzFkb8znpKxybLC4y5T9ZVcpY4awY8&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugzp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=0b78006d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1078190%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1xGL9CFUqt-_MQ-YAY1dJUYI9LWKzFkb8znpKxybLC4y5T9ZVcpY4awY8&h=2440a66c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1078190?fbclid=IwAR1xGL9CFUqt-_MQ-YAY1dJUYI9LWKzFkb8znpKxybLC4y5T9ZVcpY4awY8</a>"},{"pid":"b05e8d75d4f8e824e8caaa32379690174979162a","tid":2244433,"uid":81273,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:54:20.000Z","msg":"個民政事務專員仲大權過區會主席<br />\n執撚左佢啦"},{"pid":"236ee28b978520f4e637b2e53172679e550f5c74","tid":2244433,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:56:32.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\ntwitter有無link"},{"pid":"06430cc034d40b5b7678d7b6692e00c7781a3dbd","tid":2244433,"uid":192409,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T12:58:25.000Z","msg":"新一屆區議會都成一年, 面對民政處咁多無理打壓 咁多郁下就拉大隊離場 都唔JR 講條鐵咩"}]}